{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"BOOL","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"rotatesToMatchCamera","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When the value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"text":" and the map is rotated, the annotation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view rotates. This is also the behavior of ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","isActive":true},{"text":" objects. When the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"text":" the annotation has its rotation angle fixed.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The default value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"text":". Set this property to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"text":" if the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view’s rotation is important.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(py)rotatesToMatchCamera","symbolKind":"property","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"title":"rotatesToMatchCamera","roleHeading":"Instance Property","fragments":[{"text":"rotatesToMatchCamera","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"rotatesToMatchCamera"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L193"},"role":"symbol"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/rotatesToMatchCamera"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value that determines whether the annotation view rotates together"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with the map."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/rotatestomatchcamera"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"role":"collection","type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"title":"MLNAnnotationView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"},{"text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object that corresponds to the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"text":" protocol. When an annotation’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"offscreen.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/rotatesToMatchCamera":{"title":"rotatesToMatchCamera","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/rotatestomatchcamera","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/rotatesToMatchCamera","fragments":[{"text":"rotatesToMatchCamera","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value that determines whether the annotation view rotates together"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with the map."}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"title":"MLNAnnotation","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationImage":{"title":"MLNAnnotationImage","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationimage","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationImage"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage"},{"text":" class is responsible for presenting point-based","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotations visually on a map view. Annotation image objects wrap ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIImage"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects and may be recycled later and put into a reuse queue that is maintained","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"by the map view.","type":"text"}]}}}